							</div><!-- .comment-author .vcard -->
						</footer>
						
												<div class="ct-commentcontent">
														<p>Thanks everybody, really appreciate the feedback! The little jump is due to the fact that we don&#8217;t use CSS transitions on the elements because that did not work so smooth in Safari. We&#8217;ve added another <a href="http://tympanus.net/Development/TiltHoverEffects/index2.html" rel="nofollow">demo</a> where you can see the hover effect with CSS transitions (hard reload might be required). Thanks again for all the feedback, cheers, ML</p>
						</div>

